Name: Chris Woakes
Teams: England, Warwickshire, Sydney Thunder, Kolkata Knight Riders, Royal Challengers Bangalore, England Lions, Delhi Capitals, Team Buttler, Team Morgan, Birmingham Phoenix
Bio: By the time Chris Woakes returned from Engl's tour to South Africa at the start of 2016,he feared his Test career was over,He was 27 by then  had played six Tests,despite bowling respectably on almost every outing,he had never quite made the breakthrough  an average of 63,75 made dispiriting reading,It looked as if he may be remembered as one of Engl's nearly men
